title.narrative: Enhanced local capacity in focus provinces to develop and operationalize local child protection systems and services, includingpositive parenting, non-violent discipline

description.narrative: The local child protection system continued to improve its capacity in 27 communes of the three IECD provinces of Dien Bien, Kon Tum and Gia Lai, addressing the child protection needs of more than 3,650 children in these localities. Some 3,350 parents in 27 project communes increased their holistic parenting skills to better nurture and care for more than 6,700 children and protect these children from violence and abuse. | Status:Met | As-of Date:03/02/2022
